- role1: role=brother; obligation_level=2; situation=Be patient and understanding of each other's differences.; expectation=Building mutual respect
- role2: role=boyfriend; obligation_level=2; situation=They have argued repeatedly this week about finances.; expectation=Resolve conflicts

